{
  "stem": "27767.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] actually, the later laws which came in when we had to where the star, the yellow star.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that was in '44, when the Germans came into Hungary.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before that, different-- the laws, there were anti-Jewish laws.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like, I wasn't-- because I-- the business people, actually, were affected much more.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and-- but I was affected as anti-Semitism, and calling you names, and trying to hit you, or whatever, because you were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The rabbi-- we had a rabbi there, his first rabbi.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name Mayer Wolf Nadler.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was an older rabbi.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I was a young child, I know I went to him to study with him also.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they lived only a few-- two blocks-- I mean, two houses, actually, from our house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he had a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a grandson, which was my age.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we were very good friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so he was-- he-- he tried, always, to unify the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it, really, it was-- everybody was-- they were all friends.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were never discussions, or I mean fights or something in the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then when he died-- I remember I was a young child when he died.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was probably 62 or something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they hired another rabbi from Cluj.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "His name was [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Stroli, ?] Rabbi [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Stroli, ?] a very nice younger man with a wife and two children, young children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I know I studied with him too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So, you know, I usually went in the morning at 6:00 o'clock to study with him, or in the evening late, or shabbat, or some other free times.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
